<main>
<h2>Forgot your password?</h2>

<style>
  main {
    padding-bottom: 320px;
    padding-top: 10px;
  }

  * {
    margin: 0;
  }

  body {
    background-image: url('/images/forgot_password.jpg');
    background-size: 100%;
    background-color: #000;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    color: #fff;
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    text-align: center;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .field {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-bottom: 5px;
  }

  input[type="email"],
  input[type="password"] {
    width: 250px;
    padding: 10px;
    border-radius: 5px;
    border: 1px solid #fff;
    background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
    color: #fff;
  }

  input[type="email"]:focus,
  input[type="password"]:focus {
    outline: none;
    background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
  }

  .field .actions {
    margin-top: 20px;
  }

  input[type="submit"] {
    padding: 10px 20px;
    border-radius: 5px;
    border: none;
    background-color: #ff9900;
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: bold;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  input[type="submit"]:hover {
    background-color: #ffba33;
  }

  .links a {
    color: #ff7919;
    text-decoration: underline;
    font-size: 18px;
  }

  .footer {
    background-color: #1a1a1a;
    padding: 50px;
    text-align: center ;
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .footer img {
    max-width: 50px;
    height: auto;
    min-width: 100px;
    margin: 10px;
  }

  .container {
    margin:0 auto;
    max-width: 1400px;
  }
</style>

<%= form_for(resource, as: resource_name, url: password_path(resource_name), html: { method: :post }) do |f| %>
  <%= render "devise/shared/error_messages", resource: resource %>

  <div class="field">
    <%= f.label :email %><br />
    <%= f.email_field :email, autofocus: true, autocomplete: "email" %>
  </div>

  <div class="actions">
    <%= f.submit "Send me reset password instructions" %>
  </div>
<% end %>

<%= render "devise/shared/links" %>
</main>

<footer class="footer">
  <div class="container">
    <img src="https://cdn.cloudflare.steamstatic.com/apps/dota2/images/dota_react/dota_footer_logo.png" alt="Dota 2" />

    <img src="https://cdn.cloudflare.steamstatic.com/apps/dota2/images/dota_react/valve_logo.png" alt="Valve" />
    <p>Dota та логотип Dota є товарними знаками та/або зареєстрованими товарними знаками Valve Corporation. 2023 Valve Corporation, усі права захищені.</p>
  </div>
</footer>